{"kind": "daily", "date": "2026-07-05", "html": "<div style=\"font-family:-apple-system,'PingFang TC','Helvetica Neue',Arial,sans-serif;max-width:680px;margin:0 auto;color:#16213e;\">\n<div style=\"font-size:20px;font-weight:800;color:#1a2b4a;border-left:5px solid #5b8def;padding-left:12px;margin:0 0 18px;\">📰 每日 AI 新聞 Top 10 · 2026-07-05</div>\n<div style=\"background:#edeefb;border-left:5px solid #6b72d6;border-radius:10px;padding:13px 16px;margin-bottom:11px;\">\n  <div style=\"font-size:15px;font-weight:800;color:#16213e;line-height:1.4;\"><span style=\"color:#6b72d6;font-weight:800;\">1.</span> New Linux Kernel Privilege Escalation Flaw \"Bad Epoll\" Also Impacts Android<span style=\"display:inline-block;background:#fff;color:#5159c9;font-size:11px;font-weight:700;padding:1px 8px;border-radius:20px;margin-left:5px;\">資安</span></div>\n  <div style=\"font-size:13px;color:#5b6470;margin:3px 0 6px;\">Linux核心又被發現新的本機權限提升漏洞Bad Epoll，Android也受到影響</div>\n  <div style=\"font-size:12.5px;color:#555c68;line-height:1.55;\">Security researchers identified a use-after-free race condition in Linux's epoll subsystem, tracked as CVE-2026-46242 with a CVSS score of 7.8, allowing unprivileged processes to gain root access on affected Linux desktops, servers, and Android devices.</div>\n  <div style=\"font-size:12.5px;color:#8a909c;margin-top:3px;line-height:1.55;\">資安研究人員發現Linux核心epoll子系統存在競態條件造成的記憶體釋放後再存取漏洞（CVE-2026-46242，CVSS 7.8分），攻擊者可藉此將無特權處理程序提升為root權限，影響Linux桌面、伺服器與Android系統。</div>\n  <div style=\"font-size:12px;margin-top:7px;\"><b style=\"color:#3b424f;\">iThome</b> · <a href=\"https://www.ithome.com.tw/news/177088\" style=\"color:#3b6cf6;text-decoration:none;\">原文連結</a></div>\n</div>\n<div style=\"background:#e8f4fb;border-left:5px solid #3f97c9;border-radius:10px;padding:13px 16px;margin-bottom:11px;\">\n  <div style=\"font-size:15px;font-weight:800;color:#16213e;line-height:1.4;\"><span style=\"color:#3f97c9;font-weight:800;\">2.</span> Alibaba Reportedly Bans Employees From Using Claude Code<span style=\"display:inline-block;background:#fff;color:#2b7fb0;font-size:11px;font-weight:700;padding:1px 8px;border-radius:20px;margin-left:5px;\">政策</span></div>\n  <div style=\"font-size:13px;color:#5b6470;margin:3px 0 6px;\">阿里巴巴傳禁止員工使用Claude Code</div>\n  <div style=\"font-size:12.5px;color:#555c68;line-height:1.55;\">Alibaba has reportedly classified Anthropic's Claude Code as high-risk software and barred its employees from using the AI coding tool.</div>\n  <div style=\"font-size:12.5px;color:#8a909c;margin-top:3px;line-height:1.55;\">根據報導，阿里巴巴已將Anthropic的Claude Code列為高風險軟體，禁止員工使用這款AI程式開發工具。</div>\n  <div style=\"font-size:12px;margin-top:7px;\"><b style=\"color:#3b424f;\">TechCrunch</b> · <a href=\"https://techcrunch.com/2026/07/04/alibaba-reportedly-bans-employees-from-using-claude-code/\" style=\"color:#3b6cf6;text-decoration:none;\">原文連結</a></div>\n</div>\n<div style=\"background:#f2f6e8;border-left:5px solid #88a83f;border-radius:10px;padding:13px 16px;margin-bottom:11px;\">\n  <div style=\"font-size:15px;font-weight:800;color:#16213e;line-height:1.4;\"><span style=\"color:#88a83f;font-weight:800;\">3.</span> Midjourney Demands Hollywood Studios Disclose Their Own AI Usage<span style=\"display:inline-block;background:#fff;color:#6e8c28;font-size:11px;font-weight:700;padding:1px 8px;border-radius:20px;margin-left:5px;\">政策</span></div>\n  <div style=\"font-size:13px;color:#5b6470;margin:3px 0 6px;\">Midjourney要求好萊塢片廠揭露自身AI使用細節</div>\n  <div style=\"font-size:12.5px;color:#555c68;line-height:1.55;\">Amid an ongoing legal battle with three Hollywood studios, Midjourney is seeking to compel them to reveal how they themselves use AI tools.</div>\n  <div style=\"font-size:12.5px;color:#8a909c;margin-top:3px;line-height:1.55;\">在與三家好萊塢片廠的訴訟糾紛中，Midjourney正試圖迫使這些片廠揭露它們自己使用AI的相關細節。</div>\n  <div style=\"font-size:12px;margin-top:7px;\"><b style=\"color:#3b424f;\">TechCrunch</b> · <a href=\"https://techcrunch.com/2026/07/04/midjourney-wants-hollywood-studios-to-reveal-the-details-of-their-ai-usage/\" style=\"color:#3b6cf6;text-decoration:none;\">原文連結</a></div>\n</div>\n<div style=\"background:#f9edf6;border-left:5px solid #c56bb0;border-radius:10px;padding:13px 16px;margin-bottom:11px;\">\n  <div style=\"font-size:15px;font-weight:800;color:#16213e;line-height:1.4;\"><span style=\"color:#c56bb0;font-weight:800;\">4.</span> Fanfiction Community Divided Over Detecting AI-Generated Works<span style=\"display:inline-block;background:#fff;color:#b04b9b;font-size:11px;font-weight:700;padding:1px 8px;border-radius:20px;margin-left:5px;\">產業</span></div>\n  <div style=\"font-size:13px;color:#5b6470;margin:3px 0 6px;\">同人小說社群為揪出AI創作作品陷入內戰</div>\n  <div style=\"font-size:12.5px;color:#555c68;line-height:1.55;\">A new movement within the fanfiction community aims to root out AI-generated stories, but the detection methods being used are drawing criticism for potentially misidentifying human writers.</div>\n  <div style=\"font-size:12.5px;color:#8a909c;margin-top:3px;line-height:1.55;\">同人小說社群近期興起一股運動，試圖揪出使用生成式AI創作的作者，但所採用的偵測方法備受質疑，可能誤傷真人創作者。</div>\n  <div style=\"font-size:12px;margin-top:7px;\"><b style=\"color:#3b424f;\">The Verge</b> · <a href=\"https://www.theverge.com/tech/960854/ai-fanfiction-ao3-claude-detector\" style=\"color:#3b6cf6;text-decoration:none;\">原文連結</a></div>\n</div>\n<div style=\"background:#eef4ff;border-left:5px solid #5b8def;border-radius:10px;padding:13px 16px;margin-bottom:11px;\">\n  <div style=\"font-size:15px;font-weight:800;color:#16213e;line-height:1.4;\"><span style=\"color:#5b8def;font-weight:800;\">5.</span> OpenAI Reportedly Discussing Giving US Government a 5% Stake<span style=\"display:inline-block;background:#fff;color:#3b6cf6;font-size:11px;font-weight:700;padding:1px 8px;border-radius:20px;margin-left:5px;\">政策</span></div>\n  <div style=\"font-size:13px;color:#5b6470;margin:3px 0 6px;\">傳OpenAI有意讓美國政府取得5%持股</div>\n  <div style=\"font-size:12.5px;color:#555c68;line-height:1.55;\">The Financial Times reports OpenAI is in early talks with the U.S. government about giving it a 5% equity stake, aiming to ease political friction and share future AI wealth with the public.</div>\n  <div style=\"font-size:12.5px;color:#8a909c;margin-top:3px;line-height:1.55;\">英國金融時報報導，OpenAI正與美國政府初步討論讓政府持有5%股權的構想，希望藉此降低政治阻力並讓民眾分享AI產業未來的財富。</div>\n  <div style=\"font-size:12px;margin-top:7px;\"><b style=\"color:#3b424f;\">iThome</b> · <a href=\"https://www.ithome.com.tw/news/177061\" style=\"color:#3b6cf6;text-decoration:none;\">原文連結</a></div>\n</div>\n<div style=\"background:#ecf7ef;border-left:5px solid #4caf72;border-radius:10px;padding:13px 16px;margin-bottom:11px;\">\n  <div style=\"font-size:15px;font-weight:800;color:#16213e;line-height:1.4;\"><span style=\"color:#4caf72;font-weight:800;\">6.</span> Anthropic Launches Claude Science, an AI Workbench Aiming to Develop Drugs<span style=\"display:inline-block;background:#fff;color:#1e9e57;font-size:11px;font-weight:700;padding:1px 8px;border-radius:20px;margin-left:5px;\">產品</span></div>\n  <div style=\"font-size:13px;color:#5b6470;margin:3px 0 6px;\">Anthropic推出Claude Science，盼跨足藥物開發</div>\n  <div style=\"font-size:12.5px;color:#555c68;line-height:1.55;\">At its \"AI for Science\" briefing, Anthropic unveiled Claude Science, a new AI workbench that unifies scattered research tools and datasets and can generate figures for scientists.</div>\n  <div style=\"font-size:12.5px;color:#8a909c;margin-top:3px;line-height:1.55;\">Anthropic在「AI for Science」發表會上推出Claude Science，這款AI工作平臺整合分散的研究工具與資料集，並能為科學家自動產生圖表。</div>\n  <div style=\"font-size:12px;margin-top:7px;\"><b style=\"color:#3b424f;\">The Verge</b> · <a href=\"https://www.theverge.com/ai-artificial-intelligence/961311/anthropic-claude-science-ai-drug-development\" style=\"color:#3b6cf6;text-decoration:none;\">原文連結</a></div>\n</div>\n<div style=\"background:#f1ecfb;border-left:5px solid #8a6bd8;border-radius:10px;padding:13px 16px;margin-bottom:11px;\">\n  <div style=\"font-size:15px;font-weight:800;color:#16213e;line-height:1.4;\"><span style=\"color:#8a6bd8;font-weight:800;\">7.</span> Microsoft Launches New AI Engineering Division \"Frontier Company\"<span style=\"display:inline-block;background:#fff;color:#6b3bf6;font-size:11px;font-weight:700;padding:1px 8px;border-radius:20px;margin-left:5px;\">產業</span></div>\n  <div style=\"font-size:13px;color:#5b6470;margin:3px 0 6px;\">微軟成立新AI工程事業群Frontier Company</div>\n  <div style=\"font-size:12.5px;color:#555c68;line-height:1.55;\">Microsoft announced a new AI engineering unit, investing $2.5 billion and deploying 6,000 engineers to embed with enterprise clients and help design, deploy, and optimize their AI systems.</div>\n  <div style=\"font-size:12.5px;color:#8a909c;margin-top:3px;line-height:1.55;\">微軟宣布成立新的AI工程事業群Microsoft Frontier Company，將投入25億美元、派遣6,000名工程專家進駐企業客戶，協助設計、部署並優化AI系統。</div>\n  <div style=\"font-size:12px;margin-top:7px;\"><b style=\"color:#3b424f;\">iThome</b> · <a href=\"https://www.ithome.com.tw/news/177053\" style=\"color:#3b6cf6;text-decoration:none;\">原文連結</a></div>\n</div>\n<div style=\"background:#e8f6f5;border-left:5px solid #2bb0a6;border-radius:10px;padding:13px 16px;margin-bottom:11px;\">\n  <div style=\"font-size:15px;font-weight:800;color:#16213e;line-height:1.4;\"><span style=\"color:#2bb0a6;font-weight:800;\">8.</span> Nvidia Unveils Revenue-Sharing Model to Help AI Clouds Access GPUs<span style=\"display:inline-block;background:#fff;color:#0f9b9b;font-size:11px;font-weight:700;padding:1px 8px;border-radius:20px;margin-left:5px;\">產業</span></div>\n  <div style=\"font-size:13px;color:#5b6470;margin:3px 0 6px;\">Nvidia推出分潤新商業模式助AI雲業者取得GPU</div>\n  <div style=\"font-size:12.5px;color:#555c68;line-height:1.55;\">Nvidia introduced a new infrastructure financing model using revenue sharing and credit support to lower the barrier for AI cloud providers to build GPU-based \"AI Factories\" on its DSX architecture.</div>\n  <div style=\"font-size:12.5px;color:#8a909c;margin-top:3px;line-height:1.55;\">Nvidia推出全新AI基礎設施商業模式，透過收入分潤與信用支持機制，降低新興AI雲端業者建置採用DSX架構GPU基礎設施的資金門檻。</div>\n  <div style=\"font-size:12px;margin-top:7px;\"><b style=\"color:#3b424f;\">iThome</b> · <a href=\"https://www.ithome.com.tw/news/177052\" style=\"color:#3b6cf6;text-decoration:none;\">原文連結</a></div>\n</div>\n<div style=\"background:#fbf3e3;border-left:5px solid #d99b3f;border-radius:10px;padding:13px 16px;margin-bottom:11px;\">\n  <div style=\"font-size:15px;font-weight:800;color:#16213e;line-height:1.4;\"><span style=\"color:#d99b3f;font-weight:800;\">9.</span> Hacker Group JadePuffer Uses AI Agents to Automate Ransomware Attacks<span style=\"display:inline-block;background:#fff;color:#b9791f;font-size:11px;font-weight:700;padding:1px 8px;border-radius:20px;margin-left:5px;\">資安</span></div>\n  <div style=\"font-size:13px;color:#5b6470;margin:3px 0 6px;\">駭客團體JadePuffer利用AI代理自動化執行勒索軟體攻擊</div>\n  <div style=\"font-size:12.5px;color:#555c68;line-height:1.55;\">Security researchers uncovered a ransomware campaign fully driven by AI agents and large language models, with attackers exploiting a Langflow vulnerability for initial access.</div>\n  <div style=\"font-size:12.5px;color:#8a909c;margin-top:3px;line-height:1.55;\">資安研究人員發現一起完全由AI代理與大型語言模型驅動的勒索軟體攻擊行動，駭客利用Langflow漏洞取得初始入侵管道。</div>\n  <div style=\"font-size:12px;margin-top:7px;\"><b style=\"color:#3b424f;\">iThome</b> · <a href=\"https://www.ithome.com.tw/news/177055\" style=\"color:#3b6cf6;text-decoration:none;\">原文連結</a></div>\n</div>\n<div style=\"background:#fdeef0;border-left:5px solid #e0738a;border-radius:10px;padding:13px 16px;margin-bottom:11px;\">\n  <div style=\"font-size:15px;font-weight:800;color:#16213e;line-height:1.4;\"><span style=\"color:#e0738a;font-weight:800;\">10.</span> Google DeepMind and A24 Announce First-of-Its-Kind Research Partnership<span style=\"display:inline-block;background:#fff;color:#d83a5e;font-size:11px;font-weight:700;padding:1px 8px;border-radius:20px;margin-left:5px;\">研究</span></div>\n  <div style=\"font-size:13px;color:#5b6470;margin:3px 0 6px;\">Google DeepMind與A24電影公司宣布首創研究合作</div>\n  <div style=\"font-size:12.5px;color:#555c68;line-height:1.55;\">Google DeepMind is teaming up with acclaimed film studio A24 in a new research collaboration exploring how AI can intersect with filmmaking and creative storytelling.</div>\n  <div style=\"font-size:12.5px;color:#8a909c;margin-top:3px;line-height:1.55;\">Google DeepMind與知名電影公司A24宣布展開一項創新研究合作，探索AI如何與電影創作及說故事方式結合。</div>\n  <div style=\"font-size:12px;margin-top:7px;\"><b style=\"color:#3b424f;\">Google DeepMind</b> · <a href=\"https://deepmind.google/blog/google-deepmind-and-a24-announce-first-of-its-kind-research-partnership/\" style=\"color:#3b6cf6;text-decoration:none;\">原文連結</a></div>\n</div>\n<div style=\"text-align:center;font-size:11.5px;color:#9aa1ad;padding-top:10px;\">由 AI News Digest 從各家 RSS 自動挑選、翻譯並寄送</div>\n</div>\n"}